                     <interp inst="t18281023-264-verdict1530" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 20.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor, believing him to have been in distress.</p>
